* [[for God's sake]]
* [[for Christ's sake]]
* [[Jesus Christ!]]
* [[Christ almighty!]]
* [[for fuck's sake]]
* [[FFS]] (''abbreviation'')
* [[for crying out loud]]
* [[for goodness' sake]]
* [[Oh no!]]

